      "x": "—  Scope Lock: feature list matches request; explicit 'do NOT'; >20 files on a bugfix = red flag.",
      "sz": 15.5,
      "lvl": 0
     },
     {
      "x": "—  Finish Gate: done = evidence (test, trace), not a promise. DoD: typecheck/lint/test/e2e.",
      "sz": 15.5,
      "lvl": 0
     },
     {
      "x": "—  Error is first-class: 5 patterns — overflow · truncation · tool interrupt · infinite hook · failed compaction.",
      "sz": 15.5,
      "lvl": 0
     },
     {
      "x": "—  Circuit breaker: same tool+input >3× → block; hook depth >5 → warn; retry per error.",
      "sz": 15.5,
      "lvl": 0
     },
     {
      "x": "—  Transparent recovery: {status, summary, artifacts, next_actions, recovery_hint} — no silent fix.",
      "sz": 15.5,
      "lvl": 0
     }
